Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.35,0:01:39.02,Miyoko,,0,0,0,,Zabi ma!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.02,0:01:41.58,Miyoko,,0,0,0,,Miyoko Tanashi je tu a čaká!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.58,0:01:44.57,Miyoko,,0,0,0,,Tak ako si mi vzal mamu a ocka,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.57,0:01:47.11,Miyoko,,0,0,0,,vezmi si aj mňa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.11,0:01:48.44,Miyoko,,0,0,0,,No tak, na čo čakáš?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.44,0:01:49.34,Miyoko,,0,0,0,,Zabi ma!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.34,0:01:51.65,Miyoko,,0,0,0,,Vezmi ma do neba!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.31,0:01:55.53,Miyoko,,0,0,0,,Alebo, ak ma nedokážeš zabiť,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.22,0:02:00.11,Miyoko,,0,0,0,,vráť naspäť moje šťastie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.93,0:02:18.21,Miyoko,,0,0,0,,Vyhrala som...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.21,0:02:20.37,Miyoko,,0,0,0,,Vyhrala som!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.37,0:02:21.94,Miyoko,,0,0,0,,No tak, Bože...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.94,0:02:23.87,Miyoko,,0,0,0,,Zachráň ma!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.87,0:02:26.58,Miyoko,,0,0,0,,Vyhrala som stávku!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.97,0:02:35.96,Miyoko,,0,0,0,,Aj tak mi už nemá kto pomôcť.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.92,0:02:38.60,Miyoko,,0,0,0,,A Boh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.23,0:02:41.28,Miyoko,,0,0,0,,...neexistuje.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.42,0:02:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Našiel si ju?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.50,0:02:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Nie.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.63,0:02:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Kam sa ten zasran mohol napchať?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.71,0:03:23.35,Miyoko,,0,0,0,,Teplo...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.38,0:03:37.72,Miyoko,,0,0,0,,Ocko!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.21,0:03:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.59,0:03:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ak by ocko zomrel...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.05,0:03:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,popros o pomoc doktora Takana.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.99,0:03:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Doktora...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.43,0:03:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,...Hifumiho Takana.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.35,0:03:53.77,Miyoko,,0,0,0,,Hifumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.77,0:03:55.32,Miyoko,,0,0,0,,...Takano?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.32,0:03:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Správne.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.36,0:03:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Doktor Takano je...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.48,0:04:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,...môj profesor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.19,0:04:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Som si istý, že ti pomôže.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.68,0:04:10.05,Miyoko,,0,0,0,,Ocko!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:18.01,Miyoko,,0,0,0,,Bolo to číslo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.32,0:04:22.33,Miyoko,,0,0,0,,Telefónne číslo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.33,0:04:23.83,Miyoko,,0,0,0,,Číslo doktora Takana!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.49,0:04:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Nula.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.50,0:04:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Tri.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.09,0:04:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Dva.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Sedem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.11,0:04:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Haló?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.00,0:04:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Takano pri telefóne.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.94,0:04:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Haló?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.41,0:04:55.55,Miyoko,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.55,0:04:58.75,Miyoko,,0,0,0,,Je tam doktor Hifumi Takano?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.75,0:04:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Áno, to som ja.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.89,0:05:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kto volá?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.42,0:05:03.08,Miyoko,,0,0,0,,Prepáčte.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.08,0:05:05.44,Miyoko,,0,0,0,,Volám sa Tanashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.44,0:05:06.80,Miyoko,,0,0,0,,Miyoko Tanashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.80,0:05:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tanashi?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.94,0:05:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tanashi-san?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.20,0:05:12.18,Miyoko,,0,0,0,,Môj ocko sa volal Takemitsu Tanashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.18,0:05:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ach, áno, Tanashi-kun!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.35,0:05:18.30,Miyoko,,0,0,0,,Ocko mi povedal, aby som Vám zavolala...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.30,0:05:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dúfam že sa mu nič nestalo?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.15,0:05:25.58,Miyoko,,0,0,0,,Mama a ocko
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.58,0:05:27.68,Miyoko,,0,0,0,,zomreli pri autonehode.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.68,0:05:31.56,Miyoko,,0,0,0,,A ocko mi povedal, aby som zavolala doktorovi Takano.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.45,0:05:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rozumiem...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.24,0:05:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naozaj neviem, čo na to povedať...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.90,0:05:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tanashi-kun bol tak sympatický mladý muž...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.33,0:05:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A čo odo mňa Tanashi-kun potreboval?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.53,0:05:49.81,Miyoko,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.81,0:05:51.06,Miyoko,,0,0,0,,Ja...
