Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.37,0:20:42.70,Karaoke_SK,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Zakrývam tvoje mŕtve telo zemou,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.64,0:20:50.68,Karaoke_JAP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}sore ga kinjirareteita toshitemo
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.64,0:20:50.68,Karaoke_SK,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}aj keď viem že je to zakázané.
