Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.20,0:20:59.59,Karaoke_SK,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Spomínam na nádej ktorú som vídavala
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.20,0:21:07.41,Karaoke_JAP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}kakushikirenai yuuwaku ga atta
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.20,0:21:07.41,Karaoke_SK,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}v tvojich čistých, šťastných očiach.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.99,0:21:16.25,Karaoke_JAP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}doushite tsumi ga aru no darou
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.99,0:21:16.25,Karaoke_SK,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Prečo existujú hriechy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.25,0:21:23.22,Karaoke_JAP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}doushite batsu ga aru no darou
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.25,0:21:23.22,Karaoke_SK,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Prečo existujú tresty?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.99,0:21:32.62,Karaoke_JAP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}hori no saki wa amari ni mo shiroku
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.99,0:21:32.62,Karaoke_SK,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}To jasné svetlo na konci tunela
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.62,0:21:40.57,Karaoke_JAP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}mugen ni tsuzuku yami wo sasotta
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.62,0:21:40.57,Karaoke_SK,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}ťa pozvalo do nekonečnej tmy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.57,0:21:48.82,Karaoke_JAP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}nani mo kamo ga azayaka ni miete
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.57,0:21:48.82,Karaoke_SK,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Ale ja už už vidím všetko jasne.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.82,0:21:58.02,Karaoke_JAP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}sugu ni kieteshimau
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.82,0:21:58.02,Karaoke_SK,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}I ono čoskoro zmizne.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.95,0:22:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Kedy už konečne tú kliniku otvoria?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.17,0:22:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Písali že začnú ordinovať na budúci mesiac.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.22,0:22:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Dúfam že budú mať klimatizáciu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.42,0:22:16.30,Miyoko,,0,0,0,,Keby som vtedy nenašla tú 10 jenovú mincu...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.83,0:22:19.86,Miyoko,,0,0,0,,Aspoň za to ti musím byť vďačná.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.89,0:22:37.86,Miyoko,,0,0,0,,Takže ty si boh tejto svätyne.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.86,0:22:41.51,Hanyuu,,0,0,0,,Silná vôla ovláda osud.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.51,0:22:42.52,Miyoko,,0,0,0,,Správne.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.11,0:22:45.54,Hanyuu,,0,0,0,,Neoblomné a cieľavedomé srdce
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.54,0:22:48.21,Hanyuu,,0,0,0,,dokáže vzdorovať akémukoľvek osudu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.21,0:22:49.83,Miyoko,,0,0,0,,Presne ako hovoríš.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.70,0:22:54.47,Hanyuu,,0,0,0,,Konečne tomu rozumiem.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.47,0:22:58.34,Hanyuu,,0,0,0,,Ten osud ktorý sme nikdy nedokázali poraziť
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.34,0:23:00.77,Hanyuu,,0,0,0,,vzdoroval silou {\i1}tvojej{\i0} vôle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.26,0:23:03.22,Hanyuu,,0,0,0,,Ale viac ma už neporazíš!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.00,0:23:05.83,Hanyuu,,0,0,0,,Jeden priateľ ma niečo naučil.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.41,0:23:08.18,Hanyuu,,0,0,0,,Ukázal mi, že sila našej viery
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.18,0:23:10.82,Hanyuu,,0,0,0,,dokáže stvoriť zázrak ktorý porazí osud.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.53,0:23:15.33,Hanyuu,,0,0,0,,Už sa nenecháme poraziť silou tvojej vôle!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.39,0:23:20.61,Miyoko,,0,0,0,,Dobre!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.61,0:23:22.42,Miyoko,,0,0,0,,Tak sa mi predveď!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.42,0:23:25.90,Miyoko,,0,0,0,,Ukážem ti, koho vôla je silnejšia.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.90,0:23:30.18,Miyoko,,0,0,0,,Nevzdám sa ani kúska svojej budúcnosti!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.18,0:23:32.49,Miyoko,,0,0,0,,Ty malý škriatok!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.49,0:23:36.02,Miyoko,,0,0,0,,Vykopem ťa z tvojej vlastnej svätyne!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.76,0:23:46.75,Rika,,0,0,0,,I kind of feel like Hinamizawa has a really heavy dialect.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.75,0:23:49.70,Hanyuu,,0,0,0,,We've talked about this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.70,0:23:51.32,Rika,,0,0,0,,I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.72,0:23:58.77,Rika,,0,0,0,,Do you know the term "You damn pickle!" Satoko's uncle uses all the time means?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.77,0:24:00.87,Hanyuu,,0,0,0,,Not a clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.87,0:24:04.81,Rika,,0,0,0,,It actually comes from pickled vegetables.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.65,0:24:07.36,Hanyuu,,0,0,0,,Wait, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.36,0:24:11.67,Rika,,0,0,0,,It means a soft-like-a-pickle good-for-nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.67,0:24:13.38,Hanyuu,,0,0,0,,You have got to be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.38,0:24:14.75,Rika,,0,0,0,,I sure am!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.10,0:24:22.60,Hanyuu,,0,0,0,,Next episode: Festival Music Chapter, Part 3: The Beginning of the End.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.60,0:24:25.65,Rika,,0,0,0,,You damn pickle!
